  "body": "In the advanced settings section, if using a local build, the DEBUG flag is always active, and switching it makes no difference (i tried restarting the app). The same happens in release version, except that the log level is always INFO and it's not possible to switch the DEBUG flag\r\n\r\nI'm not entirely sure, but I believe this code might be causing the issue: https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/blob/a2aedb5c6a699c154382f75d9c5a7e6e641fa14c/src/app/boot/app_controller.nim#L137-L143\r\n\r\ncc: @chaitanyaprem ",
